{"tid":2011531,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想推介一位讀書youtuber暗室微光","createTime":"2020-05-11T05:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T01:27:34.000Z","uid":4618,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1f8a521ff7c0f1291b14db507ec960e33a9d569a","tid":2011531,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:17:23.000Z","msg":"暗室微光 Glimmer of hope<br />\n前身叫那個尋找冰塊的遙遠的下午<br />\n本職係一位記者<br />\n每條片都會用一本書嚟做主題<br />\n暫時都係社會、歷史題材<br />\n見佢初出茅廬幾有心做但冇乜人睇<br />\n如果可以搵到知音就好<br />\n<br />\n第一條片介紹咗蒙古爭取民族自決但失敗，面臨被屠殺嘅經歷<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9VShsFxX7KI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9VShsFxX7KI&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnybXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=798f1614\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9VShsFxX7KI</a><br />\n<br />\n第二條長片介紹咗日本世代之爭，兩代人價值觀矛盾<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9PtVr2W4rrE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9PtVr2W4rrE&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnybXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=8f44a64c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9PtVr2W4rrE</a><br />\n<br />\n最新一條片介紹咗60年代美國社運，其中包括地下氣象人同公民調查fbi組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ae-BD8T81aU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAe-BD8T81aU&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnybXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=fbe2b00b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ae-BD8T81aU</a>"},{"pid":"f3f2f7f29ad9cb46d446cacbd9aa4eeea2b82440","tid":2011531,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9abfa7c5c1b718785c0e5113a450ab393f99d785","tid":2011531,"uid":286927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ebb255eeb486aae34986b39a0d642c5b2da1e2","tid":2011531,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9abfa7c5c1b718785c0e5113a450ab393f99d785","ti